No. 133,

Misc.

Massengale v. Rogers, Attorney General, et al. Petitioner pro se. Solicitor General Rankin, Acting Assistant Attorney General Ryan, Harold H. Greene and David Ruibin for respondent Rogers.

Motion for leave to file petition for writ of habeas corpus denied.

Mr. Justice Stewart took no part in the consideration or decision of this application.
